{
  "texts": [
    "First, R_ref sends the decompiler output to LLM for the optimization scheme, and it gets three Yes indicating all three optimizations are required, as shown in ①.",
    "Then, R_ref sends the optimization scheme and decompiler output to the next role R_adv.",
    "The R_adv first performs the sort, and optimizations that can provide additional guidance for subsequent optimizations are given relatively higher priority.",
    "After sorting, the structure simplificaiton is in the first place.",
    "The principles of sorting are discussed in Section III-C. Next, the R_adv chooses the proper predefined prompt for the optimization and sends the prompt containing the decompiler output to LLM for the specific editing operations of the optimization."
  ]
}